snippet.title: Jag's Longplay +054+ Sega Genesis -  Star Trek - The Next Generation: Echoes From the Past
snippet.description:
An intensively involved game that has elements of action, adventure and simulation while you command the USS Enterprise.

The secret Chodak mission was completed.
